Interface TextExpression

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ComparableExpression<String>, Expression<String>, Persistable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Concat, TextFieldValue, TextLiteral

    public interface TextExpression
extends ComparableExpression<String>
    An expression that evaluates to a text (string) value.
